9368960628c7c0fab9a433281bbbbae1.query:
search(
	bm25_match(_asin.title==_title,'router',80),
	_asin.item_weight == _item_weight, op_filter(lambda e: e['?item_weight'] <= 2),
	_asin.item_weight_units == 'pounds',
        _asin.review == _review, 
        neural_match(_review.text == _review_text,"why do i have a large footprint?",5),
        neural_extract(_answers, _review.text == _review_text,"why do i have a large footprint?",2)
)

	bm25_match(_asin.title==_title,'ipad',80),
